ght=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/img_0963.jpg?w=607\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"832\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/img_0964.jpg?w=832\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"976\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/img_0957.jpg?w=976\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"622\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/img_0960.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"624\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/img_0961.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"810\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/img_0952.jpg?w=810\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"791\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/img_0949.jpg?w=791\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>纯粹容器</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"939\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/img_0948-1.jpg?w=939\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>“我找到了一个新朋友！”<br><br>“他希望我给他画一只小羊，那么他应该得到一只小羊。”</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"573\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/img_0958-1.jpg?w=573\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"909\" height=\"54\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/image.jpg?w=909\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"981\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/img_0959.jpg?w=981\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"632\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/e789b9e585b8.jpg?w=632\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"791\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/img_1010.jpg?w=791\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/img_1014.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"850\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/img_0993.jpg?w=850\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>最近买到了一个凯特帽子，还买到了一个凯特背包<img src=\"https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/mu-plugins/wpcom-smileys/twemoji/2/72x72/1f490.png\" alt=\"💐\"><img src=\"https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/mu-plugins/wpcom-smileys/twemoji/2/72x72/1f427.png\" alt=\"🐧\"></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"632\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/img_1012.jpg?w=632\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"791\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/img_1011.jpg?w=791\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"791\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/img_1009.jpg?w=791\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>住在下水道里的捡破烂猎人</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/img_1019.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>嗒哒！</figcaption></figure>",
